                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880227-32-defend371 t17880227-32-punish166"></join>
               Imprisoned six months
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury before Mr. ROSE.</p>
